Introduction

This notebook idenifies and extracts the spreadsheet data published by NHS Digital for public health topics

Identify publications

get_nhsd_pubs <- function(url){
  
  pubs <- read_html(url) %>%
    html_nodes(".title") %>%
    html_attr("href")
  
  pubs
  
  
}
test <- map(links, function(x) get_nhsd_pubs(x))
test <- flatten(test) %>% na.omit()
listviewer::jsonedit(test)

# test <- test[-1]

Identify spreadsheets

get_nhsd_sheets <- function(url){
  
  sheets <- read_html(url) %>%
    html_nodes(".extension\\.xlsx") %>%
    html_attr("href")
}
xls <- map(test, function(x) get_nhsd_sheets(x))
xls <- flatten(xls)
listviewer::jsonedit(xls)

test1 <- str_split(xls, "/")
filenames <- map(test1, 8 )
length(filenames)
